    ]
  },
  "mockData": {
    "count": 10,
    "description": "Generate 10 account merge records: 5 completed successfully, 3 in processing state, 2 failed. Include diverse scenarios: merges with prestations (5-20 records), merges with depot_garantie (2-5 records), merges with cc_comptable entries (10-50 records). Each merge should have 3-10 detail records (one per table processed) and 5-20 log entries (mix of INFO, WARNING, ERROR types). Vary merge dates over the past 30 days. Include different operators and societies."
  },
